## MODEL SELECTION — COST OPTIMIZATION

| Task | Tier | Model |
|------|------|-------|
| Boilerplate, stubs, i18n, renaming | 0 | SWE-1.5 (preferred), haiku |
| Simple single-file fixes, unit tests | 1 | gpt-4o-mini, gemini-flash |
| Standard coding, refactor, API, tests | 2 ★ | claude-sonnet ← DEFAULT |
| Architecture, deep debug, cross-module | 3 | claude-opus, gpt-4.5 |
| Novel algorithms, cross-system design | 4 | gpt-5 |

★ Always start at lowest viable tier. Escalate one tier at a time only if result is wrong.
